    {
    
    
    "type" :
    
    
    "static"
    ,
    
    "inputs" : {
    
    
    "para" :
    true,
    
    "html" :
    
    
    "             Start at the edge of the dent              <a class=\"qv qv-grafik\" href=\"\" target=\"PIWIS0e7c9f78c9a31004821edab5c05fd45f2\">-A-</a>              at 9 o'clock and work clockwise through 12 o'clock to 3 o'clock. When doing this, always remember to press the panel at as many points as possible and as close together as possible. From 3 o'clock, move further inwards and carry on through 12 o'clock to 9 o'clock. Carry out the remaining steps in this same way.         "
    
