    "html" :
    
    
    " With a dent of approx. 2 cm in diameter, it will be necessary to press the panel at around 100 – 150 points. Any point that is pressed too hard must be pushed back again before continuing. Strain can be created in the panel as a result of too many high points, with the result that the metal sheet can no longer spread out evenly."
    
